The paper deals with multi-agent reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of machine learning and artificial intelligence. The paper also discusses policy gradients, which is a popular technique in deep reinforcement learning. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are the most likely categories. The paper also deals with multi-agent systems, which falls under cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems). The paper also discusses navigation and traffic simulation, which falls under cs.RO (Robotics) and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
